snippet.title: Serious Duke 3D | Trailer
snippet.description:
Serious Duke 3D is a remake and reimagining of the first Duke Nukem 3D episode as a total conversion mod for Serious Sam Fusion. 
https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=1432570016


Trailer music: Legacy of Grabbag, by Brandon Blume
https://youtu.be/uu9vDTs0ciE , http://brandonblume.com/
+thanks to Voidpoint who own the track. https://twitter.com/voidpnt
